aley Sprite Le Mans]]\n| [[BMC A-Series engine|BMC]] 1293cc S4\n| 134\n| Clutch<br> (16hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>5.0\n| 17\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Ecurie Francorchamps]]\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} \"Beurlys\" (Jean Blaton)<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Pierre Dumay]]\n| [[Ferrari P#365 P2|Ferrari 365 P2]]\n| Ferrari 4.4L V12\n| 129\n| Engine<br> (14hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>5.0\n| 20\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} SpA [[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]] SEFAC\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Ludovico Scarfiotti]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Mike Parkes]]\n| [[Ferrari P#330 P3|Ferrari 330 P3]]\n| Ferrari 4.0L V12\n| 123\n| Accident<br> (9hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>1.15\n| 55\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 Automobiles<br>[[Alpine (car)|Alpine]]\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Andr\u00e9 de Cortanze]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} Jean-Pierre Hanrioud\n| [[Alpine A210]]\n| [[Renault]]-[[Gordini]] 1005cc S4\n| 118\n| Water pump<br> (20hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>2.0\n| 41\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Equipe Matra Sports|Matra Sport]]\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Johnny Servoz-Gavin]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jean-Pierre Beltoise]]\n| [[Matra MS620]]\n| [[British Racing Motors|BRM]] 1915cc V8\n| 112\n| Gearbox<br> (13hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>+5.0\n| 9\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Chaparral Cars]]\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Phil Hill]]<br>{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Jo Bonnier]]\n| [[Chaparral Cars#2|Chaparral 2D]]\n| [[Chevrolet]] 5.4L V8\n| 111\n| Electrics<br> (8hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>+5.0\n| 7\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Alan Mann Racing]]\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Graham Hill]]<br>{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Brian Muir (racing driver)|Brian Muir]]\n| [[Ford GT40 Mk.II]]\n| Ford 7.0L V8\n| 110\n| Front suspension<br> (8hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>2.0\n| 34\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Auguste Veuillet\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Robert Buchet<br>{{flagicon|DEU}} Gerhard 'Gerd' Koch\n| [[Porsche 906]]/6 Carrera 6\n| Porsche 1991cc F6\n| 110\n| Accident<br> (9hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>2.0\n| 42\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Equipe Matra Sports|Matra Sport]]\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jo Schlesser]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Alan Rees (racing drive