ay<br>''(private entrant)''\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Pierre Dumay]]<br>{{flagicon|BEL}} Gustave \u2018Taf\u2019 Gosselin\n| [[Dino 206 S]]\n| Ferrari 1986cc V6\n| Did not arrive\n|-\n! DNF\n| GT<br>1.6\n| 44\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Ecurie Nationale Belge|Equipe Nationale Belge]]\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} Georges Harris<br>{{flagicon|BEL}} Gerhard Langlois van Ophem\n| [[Alfa Romeo Giulia TZ]]2\n| Alfa Romeo 1570cc S4\n| Did not arrive\n|}\n\n===Class winners===\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%\"\n! Class\n! colspan=2|Prototype<br>winners\n! Class\n! colspan=2|Sports<br>winners\n! Class\n! colspan=2|GT<br>winners\n|-\n! Prototype<br>5000\n| #2 Ford GT40 Mk.II\n| Amon / McLaren *\n! Sports<br>5000\n|colspan=2|    -\n! Grand Touring<br>5000\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n|-\n! Prototype<br> 5000\n|colspan=2| no finishers\n! Sports<br> 5000\n|colspan=2| no finishers\n! Grand Touring<br> 5000\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n|-\n! Prototype<br> 4000\n|colspan=2| no finishers\n! Sports<br> 4000\n|colspan=2| no finishers\n! Grand Touring<br> 4000\n| #29 Ferrari 275 GTB<br>Competizione\n| Courage / Pike\n|-\n! Prototype<br> 3000\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n! Sports<br> 3000\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n! Grand Touring<br> 3000\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n|-\n! Prototype<br> 2000\n| #30 Porsche 906/6 LH\n| Siffert / Davis *\n! Sports<br> 2000\n| #58 Porsche 906/6\n| Stommelen / Klass *\n! Grand Touring<br> 2000\n| #35 Porsche 911 S\n| \"Franc\" / Kerguen\n|-\n! Prototype<br> 1600\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n! Sports<br> 1600\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n! Grand Touring<br> 1600\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n|-\n! Prototype<br> 1300\n| #62 Alpine A210 M64\n| Grandsire / Cella *\n! Sports<br> 1300\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n! Grand Touring<br> 1300\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n|-\n! Prototype<br> 1150\n|colspan=2| no finishers\n! Sports<br> 1150\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n! Grand Touring<br> 1150\n|colspan=2| no entrants\n|}\n* <small>'''Note''': setting a new Distance Record.</small>\n\n===Index of thermal efficiency===\n<ref name=\"Spurring 2010, p.171\">Spurring 2010, p.171</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n! Pos\n! Class\n! No\n! Team\n! Drivers\n! Chassis\n! Score\n|-\n! 1\n| P<br>1.3\n| 44\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Ecurie Savin-Calberson\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Roger Delageneste<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} Jacques Cheinisse\n| [[Alpine A210]]\n| 1.35\n|-\n! 2\n| P<br>1.3\n| 46\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 Automobiles<br>Alpine\n| {{flagicon|CHE}} Mauro Bianchi<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} Jean Vinatier\n| [[Alpine A210]]\n| 1.33\n|-\n! 3=\n| P<br>1.3\n| 45\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 Automobiles<br>Alpine\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Robert Bouharde<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} Guy Verrier\n| [[Alpine A210]]\n| 1.32\n|-\n! 3=\n| P<br>+5.0\n| 1\n| {{flagicon|USA}} Shelby American\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} Ken Miles<br>{{flagicon|NZL}} Denny Hulme\n| Ford GT40 Mk.II\n| 1.32\n|-\n! 5\n| P<br>1.3\n| 62\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 Automobiles<br>Alpine\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Henri Grandsire<br>{{flagicon|ITA}} Leo Cella\n| Alpine A210\n| 1.30\n|-\n! 6\n| P<br>+5.0\n|2\n| {{flagicon|USA}} Shelby American\n| {{flagicon|NZL}} Bruce McLaren<br>{{flagicon|NZL}} Chris Amon\n| Ford GT40 Mk.II\n| 1.24\n|-\n! 7\n| P<br>+5.0\n| 5\n| {{flagicon|USA}} Holman & Moody\n| {{flagicon|USA}} Ronnie Bucknum<br>{{flagicon|USA}} Dick Hutcherson\n| Ford GT40 Mk.II\n| 1.14\n|-\n! 8\n| P<br>2.0\n| 30\n| {{flagicon|DEU}} Porsche System<br>Engineering\n| {{flagicon|CHE}} Jo Siffert<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} Colin Davis\n| Porsche 906/6 LH\n| 1.09\n|-\n! 9\n| P<br>2.0\n| 31\n| {{flagicon|DEU}} Porsche System<br>Engineering\n| {{flagicon|DEU}} Hans Herrmann<br>{{flagicon|DEU}} Herbert Linge\n| Porsche 906/6 LH\n| 1.04\n|-\n! 10\n| P<br>2.0\n| 32\n| {{flagicon|DEU}} Porsche System<br>Engineering\n| {{flagicon|DEU}} Udo Sch\u00fctz<br>{{flagicon|ZAF|1928}} Peter de Klerk\n| Porsche 906/6 LH\n| 1.03\n|}\n* <small>'''Note''': Only the top ten positions are included in this set of standings.</small>\n\n===I