ine A210]]\n| [[Renault]]-[[Gordini]] 1296cc S4\n| 307\n|-\n! 13\n| P<br>1.3\n| 46\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 Automobiles<br>[[Alpine (car)|Alpine]]\n| {{flagicon|CHE}} Mauro Bianchi<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jean Vinatier]]\n| [[Alpine A210]]\n| [[Renault]]-[[Gordini]] 1296cc S4\n| 306\n|-\n! 14\n| GT<br>2.0\n| '''35'''\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} '''J. Franc'''<br>''(private entrant)''\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} ''' \"Franc\" (Jacques Dewes)'''<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} '''Jean Kerguen'''\n| [[Porsche 911]]S\n| Porsche 1991cc F6\n| 284\n|-\n! 15\n| P<br>1.3\n| 50\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} J-L Marnat & Cie<br>''(private entrant)''\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jean-Louis Marnat]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Claude Ballot-L\u00e9na]]\n| [[Mini Marcos]] GT 2+2\n| [[British Motor Corporation|BMC]] 1287cc S4\n| 258\n|}\n\n===Did not finish===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n! Pos\n! Class\n! No\n! Team\n! Drivers\n! Chassis\n! Engine\n! Laps\n! Reason\n|-\n! DNF\n| S<br>2.0\n| 33\n| {{flagicon|DEU}} [[Porsche in motorsport|Porsche System]]<br>Engineering\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Peter Gregg (racing driver)|Peter Gregg]]<br>{{flagicon|SWE}} Sten Axelsson\n| [[Porsche 906]]/6 Carrera 6\n| Porsche 1991cc F6\n| 321\n| Engine<br> (24hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>+5.0\n| 3\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Carroll Shelby International|Shelby American]]\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Dan Gurney]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Jerry Grant]]\n| [[Ford GT40 Mk.II]]\n| Ford 7.0L V8\n| 257\n| Radiator<br> (18hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>1.3\n| 49\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Donald Healey Motor Company]]\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Paddy Hopkirk]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} Andrew Hedges\n| [[Austin-Healey Sprite]]\n| [[BMC A-Series engine|BMC]] 1293cc S4\n| 237\n| Head gasket<br> (21hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| S<br>5.0\n| 14\n| {{flagicon|CHE}} [[Scuderia Filipinetti]]\n| {{flagicon|CHE}} Dieter Spoerry<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Peter Sutcliffe (racing driver)|Peter Sutcliffe]]\n| [[Ford GT40]]\n| Ford 4.7L V8\n| 233\n| Accident<br> (17hr)\n|-\n! DNF\n| P<br>5.0\n| 21\n| 