mericana|2020]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://global.espn.com/football/conmebol-recopa-sudamericana/story/4061590/flamengos-recopa-win-over-independiente-a-stepping-stone-to-more-glory|title=Flamengo's Recopa win over Independiente a stepping stone to more glory|newspaper=[[ESPN]]|first=Tim|last=Vickery|date=27 February 2020|accessdate=27 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n===International===\n'''Brazil'''\n*[[Summer Olympic Games|Olympic Gold Medal]]: [[Football at the 2016 Summer Olympics|2016]]\n\n===Individual===\n* [[Copa do Brasil]] Top scorer: [[2014 Copa do Brasil|2014]], [[2015 Copa do Brasil|2015]], [[2018 Copa do Brasil|2018]]\n* [[Bola de Ouro|Bola de Prata]] Best Newcomer: [[Bola de Ouro#2015|2015]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://revistaplacar.uol.com.br/noticias/bola-de-prata/gabriel-ganha-o-premio-despertar-da-forca-como-revelacao-do-brasileiro-2015.phtml |title=Gabriel ganha o pr\u00eamio 'Despertar da For\u00e7a' como revela\u00e7\u00e3o do Brasileiro 2015 |date=7 December 2015 |website=[[Placar]] |language=pt |trans-title=Gabriel wins 'The Force Awakens' prize as the best newcomer of Brasileiro 2015 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208123620/http://revistaplacar.uol.com.br/noticias/bola-de-prata/gabriel-ganha-o-premio-despertar-da-forca-como-revelacao-do-brasileiro-2015.phtml#.VmYUK7grLDc |archive-date=8 December 2015 |access-date=7 December 2015}}</ref>\n* [[Campeonato Paulista]] Team of the Tear: [[2016 Campeonato Paulista|2016]],<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://globoesporte.globo.com/sp/futebol/campeonato-paulista/noticia/2016/05/santos-domina-selecao-do-paulistao-audax-emplaca-dois-e-mais-o-tecnico.html |title=Santos domina sele\u00e7\u00e3o do Paulist\u00e3o; Audax emplaca dois e mais o t\u00e9cnico |date=9 May 2016 |website=Globo Esporte |language=pt |trans-title=Santos dominate the ''Paulist\u00e3o'' team of the year; Audax include two and the manager |access-date=9 May 2016}}</ref> [[2018 Campeonato Paulista|2018]]\n* [[Bola de Ouro|Bola de Prata]]: [[Bola de Ouro#Bola de Prata|2018]], [[Bola de Ouro#Bola de Prata|2019]]<ref name=\":Bola de Prata 2019\"></ref>\n* [[Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A]] Top scorer: [[2018 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A|2018]], [[2019 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A|2019]]\n* [[Pr\u00eamio Craque do Brasileir\u00e3o|Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A Team of the Year]]: [[2018 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A|2018]], [[2019 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A|2019]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.goal.com/br/not%C3%ADcias/premio-craque-do-brasileirao-2019-veja-a-selecao-e-quem-foi/xa3190kr0z0o18za8d5v2nng3 |title=Pr\u00eamio Craque do Brasileir\u00e3o 2019: veja a sele\u00e7\u00e3o e quem foi premiado |date=9 December 2019 |publisher=Goal.com |language=pt-BR |access-date=10 December 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Campeonato Carioca]] Team of the Year: [[2019 Campeonato Carioca|2019]]<ref name=\":1\"></ref>\n* [[Copa Libertadores]] Top scorer: [[2019 Copa Libertadores|2019]]\n* [[Bola de Ouro]]: [[Bola de Ouro#2019|2019]]<ref name=\":Bola de Prata 2019\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.espn.com.br/futebol/bola-de-prata/artigo/_/id/6389730/bola-de-prata-veja-como-ficou-a-selecao-do-campeonato-brasileiro-2019 |title=Bola de Prata: veja como ficou a sele\u00e7\u00e3o do Campeonato Brasileiro 2019 |date=9 December 2019 |publisher=ESPN Brasil |language=pt |access-date=9 December 2019}}</ref>\n*[[South American Footballer of the Year]]: 2019<ref name=\":0\" />\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n*{{NFT player|pid=64510}}\n*{{Soccerway}}\n\n{{Clube de Regatas do Flamengo squad}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title=Brazil squads\n|bg=#FFDF00\n|fg=#008000\n|bordercolor=blue\n|list1=\n{{Brazil squad Copa Am\u00e9rica Centenario}}\n{{Brazil men's football squad 2016 Summer Olympics}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n|title= Awards\n|bg= gold\n|fg= navy\n|list1=\n{{Copa do Brasil top scorers}}\n{{Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A top scorers}}\n{{Copa Libertadores to