. Foley\n| '''Christopher R. Foley'''\n| align=\"right\"| 175,825\n| align=\"right\"| 98.91%\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" | \n|-\n| 25\n| Stephanie Rothstein\n| '''Stephanie Rothstein'''\n| align=\"right\"| 168,070\n| align=\"right\"| 98.83%\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" | \n|-\n| 31\n| Paul Rifelj\n| '''Hannah C. Dugan'''\n| align=\"right\"| 132,461\n| align=\"right\"| 64.90%\n| Paul Rifelj\n| align=\"right\"| 70,098\n| align=\"right\"| 34.35%\n| \n|-\n| 34\n| Glenn H. Yamahiro\n| '''Glenn H. Yamahiro'''\n| align=\"right\"| 167,132\n| align=\"right\"| 98.83%\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" | \n|-\n| 44\n| Daniel L. Konkol\n| '''Gwen Connolly'''\n| align=\"right\"| 167,479\n| align=\"right\"| 98.93%\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" | \n|-\n| 45\n| Michelle Ackerman Havas\n| '''Jean Marie Kies'''\n| align=\"right\"| 100,409\n| align=\"right\"| 49.86%\n| Michelle Ackerman Havas \n| align=\"right\"| 99,225\n| align=\"right\"| 49.28%\n| \n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Monroe\n| 2\n| Mark L. Goodman\n| '''Mark L. Goodman'''\n| align=\"right\"| 11,260\n| align=\"right\"| 99.68%\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" | \n|-\n| 3\n| J. David Rice\n| '''J. David Rice'''\n| align=\"right\"| 11,100\n| align=\"right\"| 99.61%\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" | \n|-\n! Oconto\n| 2\n| Jay Conley\n| '''Jay Conley'''\n| align=\"right\"| 11,890\n| align=\"right\"| 100.00%\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" | \n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" | Pierce\n| Joseph D. Boles\n| '''Joseph D. Boles'''\n| align=\"right\"| 10,309\n| align=\"right\"| 100.00%\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" | \n|-\n! Portage\n| 2\n| Robert J. Shannon\n| '''Robert J. Shannon'''\n| align=\"right\"| 12,551\n| align=\"right\"| 54.22%\n| Trish Baker \n| align=\"right\"| 10,515\n| align=\"right\"| 45.42%\n| David R. Knaapen <br />Jared Redfield\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Racine\n| 2\n| Eugene A. Gasiorkiewicz\n| '''Eugene A. Gasiorkiewicz'''\n| align=\"right\"| 40,407\n| align=\"right\"| 100.00%\n| colspan=\"4\" align=\"center\" | 